num=int(input("Enter a number: "))
order=len(str(num))
sum=0
temp=num
while temp>0:
    N=temp%10
    temp=temp//10
    sum=sum+pow(N,order)
    if(sum==num):
        print(num,"is an Armstrong Number.")
    else:
        print(num,"is not an Armstrong Number.")
Output:-
Enter a number: 371
371 is not an Armstrong Number.
